<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="basic_ios" id="basic_ios">basic_ios</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>

<img src="http://www.cppreference.com/wiki/lib/exe/fetch.php?hash=aa24a6&amp;media=http%3A%2F%2Fchart.apis.google.com%2Fchart%3Fcht%3Dgv%253Adot%26chl%3Ddigraph%2520inheritance%2520%257B%250A%2520%2520graph%2520%255Bdpi%253D%252255%2522%255D%250A%2520%2520node%2520%255Bshape%2520%253D%2520box%252C%2520fontsize%253D14%255D%253B%2520%2520%2520%2520%250A%250A%2520%2520base%2520%255Blabel%2520%253D%2520%2522ios_base%2522%255D%253B%2520%250A%2520%2520ios%2520%255Blabel%2520%253D%2520%2522basic_ios%253CChar%252C%2520Traits%253E%2522%252C%2520style%253Dfilled%255D%253B%2520%250A%250A%2520%2520base%2520-%253E%2520ios%253B%250A%257D" class="mediaright" alt=""/>
</p>

<p>
<a href="../../todo" class="wikilink1" title="todo">todo</a>
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp"><span class="co2">#include &lt;ios&gt;</span>
&nbsp;
<span class="kw2">template</span><span class="sy1">&lt;</span>
    <span class="kw2">class</span> Char,
    <span class="kw2">class</span> Traits <span class="sy1">=</span> char_traits<span class="sy1">&lt;</span>Char<span class="sy1">&gt;</span>
<span class="sy1">&gt;</span> <span class="kw2">class</span> basic_ios<span class="sy4">;</span>         <span class="co1">//inherits ios_base</span></pre>
<p>
The class <code>basic_ios</code> provides facilities for interfacing with objects that have <a href="../basic_streambuf/start" class="wikilink1" title="io:basic_streambuf:start">basic_streambuf</a> interface. Character type dependent formatting settings are also stored in this class. This class inherits <code>ios_base</code> class. Two specializations for common character types are also provided:
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp"><span class="kw4">typedef</span> basic_ios<span class="sy1">&lt;</span><span class="kw4">char</span><span class="sy1">&gt;</span> ios<span class="sy4">;</span>
<span class="kw4">typedef</span> basic_ios<span class="sy1">&lt;</span><span class="kw4">wchar_t</span><span class="sy1">&gt;</span> wios<span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

<br/>


</p>

</div>

